<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> If CH had never existed the whole game would be diffrent. I doubt you would see mobs with 30 bajillion hp just to challange the players. Uber mobs would have been tuned around the next best heal.<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
People do Naggy/Vox without CH chains. The only reason they're making yard trash mobs with 20k hitpoints that double for 250 is because of CH. Baldrik's opinion, however valid for the contemporary, doesn't consider that if CH hadn't been put into the game, things would have been very different. Look at the Kunark mobs/dragons... very few of them actually require a CH chain. Can kill Trakanon or Sev without a single CH being cast. (Almost have to on Trak because his AE means you need lots of spots.)<br>
<br>
